WEBVTT

10:27.478 --> 10:29.478
Yeah, Mamaji,
he does that.

10:29.480 --> 10:31.613
When I told him
about my abandoned book,
he said...

10:31.615 --> 10:33.549
(IMITATES INDIAN ACCENT)
"So, a Canadian
who's come to French India

10:33.551 --> 10:35.617
"in search of a story."

10:35.619 --> 10:38.821
"Well, my friend,
I know an Indian
in French Canada...

10:38.823 --> 10:41.724
"with the most
incredible story to tell.
